bio:
Mul gro-Largash, an orc man, works as a miner in Gloombound Mine, within the territory owned by the Narzulbur orc stronghold.
The Narzulbur stronghold's lands are located at the base of the Velothi mountains, southeast of the city of Windhelm.
Mul recently left the Largashbur stronghold with his brother, Gadba. Their plan is to get rich from mining, then go back home to Largashbur and take over the stronghold. Mul and Gadba often discuss which one of them should be the chief once they return to Largashbur.
name: Mul gro-Largash
